WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.910
[Episode 14]

02:51.650 --> 02:52.650
One.

02:54.079 --> 02:55.970
Given Chong Zhao's current situation,

02:56.000 --> 02:58.190
it'll be difficult for him to break through the encirclement of the Outlander Palace.

02:58.310 --> 03:00.400
Fan Yue has taken the last pill today.

03:00.420 --> 03:02.430
His memory might return tonight.

03:02.530 --> 03:03.410
Two.

03:03.870 --> 03:05.120
As long as we can hold on until then,

03:05.140 --> 03:06.330
there will be a chance,

03:06.360 --> 03:07.570
and Chong Zhao and the others

03:07.590 --> 03:08.430
will survive too.

03:09.860 --> 03:10.610
Three.

03:10.640 --> 03:11.150
Fan Yue!

03:11.170 --> 03:11.750
Fan Yue!

03:17.400 --> 03:18.410
I choose Fan Yue.

03:25.010 --> 03:26.170
See?

03:26.320 --> 03:27.640
At the critical moment,

03:27.670 --> 03:29.310
Bai Shuo eventually chose Fan Yue.

03:29.329 --> 03:31.420
What she cares about the most has never been you.

03:31.450 --> 03:32.320
You've never been

03:32.340 --> 03:33.710
in her heart.

03:38.030 --> 03:38.990
Chong Zhao,

03:39.560 --> 03:40.890
you should see that now.

03:41.030 --> 03:43.160
No matter whether it's Eternals or Humans,

03:43.180 --> 03:44.180
you've been protecting them,

03:44.210 --> 03:45.890
but when have they ever truly protected you?

03:45.910 --> 03:48.060
When have they ever cared about your thoughts?

03:48.290 --> 03:49.780
It would be better to join the Cold Spring Palace.

03:49.920 --> 03:51.360
Not only can you survive,

03:51.390 --> 03:53.640
but you can also do

03:53.660 --> 03:55.450
whatever you want from then on.

03:57.040 --> 03:59.140
Lady Fu Ling, have you enjoyed yourself?

04:02.980 --> 04:04.200
Master!

04:06.240 --> 04:07.400
General, it's all thanks to

04:07.400 --> 04:08.840
the elixir you made for me

04:08.840 --> 04:10.720
that I can temporarily use spiritual power.

04:10.750 --> 04:12.970
I've been researching this elixir for many years.

04:13.000 --> 04:14.230
It's only today

04:14.250 --> 04:15.300
that I managed to succeed in making it.

04:16.390 --> 04:17.370
My Lady,

04:17.490 --> 04:19.010
it's time to get down to business.

04:23.190 --> 04:24.710
What do you want?

04:25.130 --> 04:27.490
You should return the spiritual bone you owe Hua Yong now.

04:27.620 --> 04:29.250
As for the interest from these seven years,

04:29.280 --> 04:31.010
your life will serve as payment.

04:59.540 --> 05:01.220
Using the Heart Flame as the catalyst,

05:01.240 --> 05:02.560
and the bloodline as the sacrifice,

05:03.060 --> 05:04.590
the fusion of Eternal and demon blood

05:05.190 --> 05:06.590
can forge a deity!

05:06.970 --> 05:07.880
The Outlanders' City

05:09.010 --> 05:11.490
will soon have its own deity!

05:11.520 --> 05:12.470
Creating a deity?

05:13.250 --> 05:14.740
The Contemplation Stone is a divine object

05:14.770 --> 05:16.710
from ancient times, belonging to Goddess Xingyue of the Lunar Race.

05:16.890 --> 05:18.840
60,000 years ago, during the Divine War, the deities perished,

05:18.860 --> 05:20.420
the Contemplation Stone was damaged,

05:20.450 --> 05:21.940
and no one has been able to activate it since.

05:22.100 --> 05:23.580
-Humans
-Boss,

05:23.610 --> 05:25.930
-are the most complex beings in the world.
-are you an Eternal?

05:25.950 --> 05:27.730
How dare you ask me

05:27.840 --> 05:29.130
if I am an Eternal?

05:30.570 --> 05:31.800
Silver Sea?

05:31.820 --> 05:32.850
Is this the legendary

05:32.880 --> 05:33.930
Lunar Hidden Sea?

05:33.950 --> 05:35.220
How to activate the Contemplation Stone?

05:35.340 --> 05:36.960
Divine visions.

05:37.700 --> 05:39.250
The Contemplation Stone is a divine object.

05:39.750 --> 05:40.960
To reactivate the Contemplation Stone,

05:41.220 --> 05:42.210
we must gather

05:42.240 --> 05:46.370
the Five Contemplations—love, hate, kill, greed,

05:46.390 --> 05:47.510
and kindness.

05:50.680 --> 05:51.310
Let go of me!

05:51.310 --> 05:52.080
Young Master?

05:53.170 --> 05:54.150
These bastards!

05:54.170 --> 05:55.370
Why did you get captured too?

05:55.909 --> 05:57.409
Something major happened in the Underground Palace.

05:57.440 --> 05:58.240
Tonight,

05:58.260 --> 05:59.159
all the Eternals and demons

05:59.159 --> 06:00.400
will become Hua Yong's sacrifices.

06:02.190 --> 06:03.430
What? Sacrifices?

06:03.460 --> 06:04.110
Sacrifice?

07:42.550 --> 07:43.740
I did it.

07:44.860 --> 07:45.800
Hua Yong,

07:46.370 --> 07:47.260
come here.

07:47.560 --> 07:48.980
I'm your master.

07:56.560 --> 07:57.710
Didn't the master say that

07:57.730 --> 07:59.100
even if Hua Yong becomes a deity,

07:59.330 --> 08:00.570
he would still recognize me as his master

08:00.600 --> 08:01.720
and work for me?

08:01.740 --> 08:02.960
Why is there no response?

08:03.250 --> 08:04.820
That's because...

08:04.840 --> 08:05.660
the formation was wrong.

08:05.870 --> 08:06.770
The formation was wrong?

08:10.000 --> 08:12.200
The formation was wrong? The formation was wrong?

08:23.540 --> 08:24.980
What Grand Master taught you

08:25.010 --> 08:26.860
is not a formation to create a deity,

08:26.880 --> 08:28.230
but a formation to kill.

08:28.460 --> 08:29.630
Gathering the will to kill

08:29.660 --> 08:30.970
and creating a killing weapon.

08:31.010 --> 08:32.080
And Hua Yong

08:32.100 --> 08:34.110
happens to be that weapon.

08:39.330 --> 08:40.270
Wu Zhao,

08:40.350 --> 08:41.870
actually, from the beginning,

08:41.970 --> 08:42.870
you were just a tool

08:42.890 --> 08:44.770
that could be discarded at any time.

09:01.000 --> 09:02.000
Crawl! Crawl!

09:02.020 --> 09:02.480
Crawl!

09:02.500 --> 09:03.810
Crawl harder!

09:03.910 --> 09:05.350
Crawl! Crawl!

09:05.370 --> 09:06.150
Crawl!

09:06.150 --> 09:08.200
Keep crawling!

09:08.200 --> 09:09.200
Why did you stop?

09:09.200 --> 09:11.870
-Crawl! Crawl!
-Keep crawling!

09:18.130 --> 09:21.690
♫Across thousands of miles♫

09:20.080 --> 09:21.410
The bun is dirty.

09:21.430 --> 09:22.720
It can't be eaten now.

09:22.940 --> 09:24.130
My name is Mei Han.

09:24.250 --> 09:25.300
What's your name?

09:26.550 --> 09:27.950
It's so cold outside.

09:26.670 --> 09:31.230
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

09:27.970 --> 09:29.130
Why don't you...

09:29.330 --> 09:31.060
come home with me?

09:33.910 --> 09:41.070
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

09:42.270 --> 09:46.690
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

09:47.170 --> 09:49.320
Why Hua Yong of all people?

09:49.340 --> 09:51.060
It was all thanks to you.

09:51.210 --> 09:52.370
Hua Yong has undergone a mutation.

09:52.390 --> 09:54.150
He's the best vessel for killing intent.

09:54.180 --> 09:55.640
He'll grow strong enough

09:55.660 --> 09:57.460
to pull out the Outlander King's Sword.

09:57.490 --> 09:59.180
Your goal is not in the Outlanders' City.

09:59.200 --> 10:01.110
What's the use of pulling out the Outlander King's Sword?

10:01.920 --> 10:04.070
Of course, it's to open your heart

10:04.090 --> 10:05.450
and obtain the Contemplation Stone.

10:06.340 --> 10:07.890
This Outlander King's Sword

10:07.920 --> 10:09.080
was forged by the first King of Outlanders

10:09.080 --> 10:11.480
using meteoric iron imbued with divine power.

10:11.500 --> 10:12.790
No other weapon can do it,

10:12.790 --> 10:14.320
but this sword can.

10:16.240 --> 10:17.040
Hua Yong,

10:17.070 --> 10:18.060
pull out the sword.

10:27.880 --> 10:28.400
Fu Ling,

10:28.430 --> 10:29.480
stop him!

10:32.090 --> 10:33.860
Using a divine sword to get the divine stone.

10:33.880 --> 10:35.140
Dying here today

10:35.170 --> 10:36.450
is your fate.

10:50.640 --> 10:51.690
Shuo!

11:20.900 --> 11:21.860
Hua Yong!

11:22.230 --> 11:23.200
Hua Yong!

12:05.540 --> 12:06.350
Killing Contemplation.

12:45.860 --> 12:47.260
The Outlanders' City restricts magic.

12:47.300 --> 12:49.150
How can you still use spiritual power?

12:49.180 --> 12:50.900
The biggest mistake you made

12:51.640 --> 12:53.190
was daring to harm my girl.

13:11.790 --> 13:12.860
What happened?

13:18.310 --> 13:19.870
Why is the Outlanders' City shaking?

13:35.500 --> 13:36.320
Shuo!

13:39.020 --> 13:39.860
Zhao!

14:05.570 --> 14:06.710
The Underground Palace is about to collapse!

14:06.740 --> 14:08.040
How can we stop the collapse?

14:08.060 --> 14:10.120
We need to put the Outlander King's Sword back into its sword stand!

14:26.790 --> 14:32.090
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

14:34.870 --> 14:40.480
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

14:43.050 --> 14:50.040
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

14:50.680 --> 14:55.850
♫I'm your wanderer♫

15:00.850 --> 15:02.740
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

15:02.840 --> 15:04.990
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

15:05.270 --> 15:06.990
♫My love brought tears♫

15:07.070 --> 15:08.930
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

15:09.300 --> 15:11.030
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

15:11.390 --> 15:12.570
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

15:12.720 --> 15:14.420
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

15:15.000 --> 15:16.370
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

15:17.010 --> 15:18.030
Is this...

15:17.290 --> 15:18.780
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

15:18.270 --> 15:19.910
formed by the power of the Outlander King's Sword?

15:19.140 --> 15:20.840
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

15:21.070 --> 15:23.140
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

15:23.380 --> 15:25.210
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

15:25.390 --> 15:27.100
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

15:27.450 --> 15:29.420
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

15:29.670 --> 15:31.390
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

15:31.550 --> 15:33.890
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

15:55.450 --> 15:56.240
Fan Yue!

15:56.640 --> 15:57.450
Fan Yue!

15:58.090 --> 15:58.870
Master!

16:05.020 --> 16:06.490
Aren't you a Demon King?

16:06.570 --> 16:08.000
How could a Demon King die?

16:08.720 --> 16:09.520
Fan Yue!

16:10.090 --> 16:10.780
Fan Yue!

16:12.230 --> 16:13.070
Fan Yue!

16:16.570 --> 16:17.570
Fan Yue!

16:18.520 --> 16:19.300
Fan Yue?

16:19.450 --> 16:20.260
Fan Yue?

16:21.910 --> 16:23.510
Fan Yue? Fan Yue!

16:23.730 --> 16:24.780
Stop shaking me.

16:30.130 --> 16:32.130
I'm just a little tired.

16:33.280 --> 16:34.090
I want to take a nap.

16:50.680 --> 16:52.140
You have tamed the Outlander King's Sword.

16:52.990 --> 16:54.670
The spirit of the Outlander King's Sword has turned into a ring and recognized you as its master.

16:55.150 --> 16:56.110
Bai Shuo,

16:56.690 --> 16:58.530
you can become the new King of Outlanders.

16:59.210 --> 17:00.910
I never wanted to be a king.

17:03.150 --> 17:04.910
I just want to walk my own path.

17:08.319 --> 17:10.109
It's a good thing if she takes the Outlander King's Ring.

17:10.910 --> 17:12.220
From now on, this city

17:12.240 --> 17:14.349
will no longer be caught up in the struggle for power.

17:14.480 --> 17:15.510
Hua Yong,

17:16.290 --> 17:18.020
you can walk your own path now.

17:23.270 --> 17:26.210
[Sihai Inn]

17:27.200 --> 17:28.390
[Rejuvenation Pill]

17:44.010 --> 17:46.290
The Formation Key to Rong Xian's realm of resentment has been removed,

17:46.310 --> 17:47.750
and the city's barrier has been opened.

17:47.780 --> 17:49.280
Nan Wan has also brought the Wutong Spirit Pill

17:49.310 --> 17:50.750
back to his younger brother.

17:50.770 --> 17:51.830
We can leave now.

17:52.280 --> 17:53.520
The Outlanders' City restricts magic.

17:54.150 --> 17:56.240
Why was he able to unleash spiritual power?

17:56.370 --> 17:57.320
Why did he

17:57.340 --> 17:58.620
become like this?

17:59.090 --> 18:00.150
I'm not sure either.

18:00.310 --> 18:02.220
Ask him when he wakes up.

18:06.340 --> 18:07.890
Take care of him.

18:07.910 --> 18:08.440
I'll go...

18:08.440 --> 18:09.640
You want to save Chong Zhao?

18:11.640 --> 18:13.120
He was taken by Fu Ling?

18:13.420 --> 18:15.610
I've already sent a disciple named Le Zhu

18:15.630 --> 18:16.670
to inform Lanling.

18:17.160 --> 18:18.910
Chong Zhao is the head disciple of Lanling.

18:19.050 --> 18:20.510
It would be much more effective

18:20.540 --> 18:21.710
to have the Five Eternals of Jin Yao save him.

18:24.090 --> 18:26.710
Actually, you don't need to worry so much about his safety.

18:27.070 --> 18:28.880
It seems someone would protect him.

18:30.190 --> 18:31.330
What do you mean?

18:31.520 --> 18:34.280
In the Underground Palace, the demonic flower armor that protected Chong Zhao

18:34.300 --> 18:36.430
was transformed from Fu Ling's protective demon flower.

18:36.840 --> 18:38.490
What kind of bond do you think

18:39.080 --> 18:41.290
could make Fu Ling willing to save him like that?

18:43.180 --> 18:44.210
Besides,

18:44.500 --> 18:45.980
there's someone here who needs you more.

18:52.120 --> 18:52.920
Tian Huo,

18:53.850 --> 18:54.890
someone is looking for you outside.

18:55.080 --> 18:55.720
Who is it?

19:33.900 --> 19:34.790
I'm sorry,

19:35.610 --> 19:36.480
Hua Yong.

19:37.530 --> 19:38.450
Sister.

19:38.470 --> 19:40.750
It's because of me that you had to endure so much pain.

19:42.120 --> 19:43.620
If I had come back earlier

19:43.640 --> 19:44.790
to face everything,

19:47.390 --> 19:48.560
and if I

19:49.370 --> 19:50.610
had trusted you back then,

19:51.940 --> 19:53.580
maybe Father wouldn't have...

19:54.350 --> 19:55.620
None of this is your fault.

19:56.300 --> 19:57.750
When we were children,

19:58.290 --> 19:59.670
I said I would protect you.

20:00.980 --> 20:02.350
I failed.

20:04.550 --> 20:05.110
No.

20:07.220 --> 20:08.740
You've always been protecting me.

20:12.080 --> 20:13.520
From the very beginning,

20:16.130 --> 20:17.720
you were the best person.

20:22.890 --> 20:23.810
Sister,

20:23.840 --> 20:24.860
are you still leaving?

20:27.120 --> 20:28.680
I have someone I must protect.

20:29.850 --> 20:31.680
But I'll come back often to see you.

20:34.580 --> 20:35.830
What are your plans

20:35.880 --> 20:36.850
for the future?

20:37.160 --> 20:38.880
The Outlanders' City needs to be rebuilt.

20:38.910 --> 20:40.190
I want to rebuild it

20:40.210 --> 20:41.340
with my people.

20:41.370 --> 20:43.130
Does everyone really not plan to leave?

20:44.430 --> 20:46.040
We used to be discriminated against,

20:46.060 --> 20:47.170
so we harbored resentment

20:47.200 --> 20:48.470
and felt inferior.

20:48.500 --> 20:50.490
We always wanted to change the way Eternals and demons viewed us

20:50.520 --> 20:51.430
and have them accept us.

20:51.650 --> 20:52.690
But now I understand that

20:53.090 --> 20:54.240
the meaning of the Outlanders' existence

20:54.270 --> 20:55.470
isn't decided by others,

20:55.510 --> 20:56.700
but by ourselves.

20:56.730 --> 20:58.450
As long as we live confidently

20:58.470 --> 20:59.080
and with integrity,

20:59.110 --> 21:00.590
we don't need to care about how other races view us.

21:01.260 --> 21:03.220
Moreover, the divine power of the Contemplation Stone

21:03.250 --> 21:04.810
has now merged into the Outlander King's Sword,

21:05.570 --> 21:07.050
allowing the Outlanders' City to continue forever.

21:07.080 --> 21:08.420
Our people are more willing to stay

21:08.440 --> 21:09.440
and rebuild the city.

21:10.240 --> 21:11.450
You've really grown up.

21:11.480 --> 21:12.760
Aren't you the same?

21:13.870 --> 21:15.100
Actually, I'm here

21:15.180 --> 21:17.470
to ask Ms. Bai to become the king of the Outlanders' City.

21:18.120 --> 21:19.980
The spirit of the Outlander King's Sword recognized Ms. Bai as its master,

21:20.010 --> 21:21.200
and she saved the Outlanders' City.

21:21.230 --> 21:22.190
We all hope

21:22.210 --> 21:23.910
she will become the new king of the Outlanders' City.

21:24.810 --> 21:26.710
The Outlanders' City already has a new king.

21:30.790 --> 21:31.760
It's you.

21:32.590 --> 21:33.640
How could I?

21:33.660 --> 21:34.730
Why not?

21:34.820 --> 21:35.590
Compassion,

21:35.590 --> 21:36.250
justice,

21:36.270 --> 21:36.880
and mercy

21:36.910 --> 21:38.680
are the most important qualities for a ruler.

21:38.700 --> 21:39.830
You have them all.

21:40.070 --> 21:42.380
You love your people more than anyone else.

21:42.410 --> 21:43.300
Compared to me,

21:43.320 --> 21:45.190
You're more suited to be the King of Outlanders.

21:47.520 --> 21:48.280
Hua Yong,

21:48.920 --> 21:50.510
I believe you can lead the Outlanders' City

21:50.510 --> 21:52.030
down a different path.

21:52.480 --> 21:53.400
Besides,

21:53.430 --> 21:55.270
I have things I must do

21:55.920 --> 21:57.120
and can't stay here.

21:58.040 --> 21:58.940
Ms. Bai,

21:59.120 --> 21:59.770
Sister,

21:59.910 --> 22:01.700
I will protect this city well.

22:02.040 --> 22:03.140
If one day,

22:03.160 --> 22:04.540
you're tired from your travels,

22:04.570 --> 22:05.810
remember,

22:05.830 --> 22:07.080
this city is your home too.

22:29.860 --> 22:30.520
Fan Yue!

22:30.740 --> 22:31.520
Wait a moment.

22:31.610 --> 22:32.370
You go out first.

22:32.390 --> 22:32.990
Wait.

22:33.020 --> 22:34.170
-Go.
-What's wrong with him?

22:34.670 --> 22:35.500
Master.

22:35.880 --> 22:36.400
Master!

22:36.400 --> 22:37.170
Fan Yue!

22:49.180 --> 22:50.600
What should we do?

22:50.630 --> 22:51.390
Another one has fallen.

22:51.410 --> 22:52.870
Now there are only two stars left.

22:52.900 --> 22:54.140
Can Master hold on until the Five Thoughts are gathered?

22:54.160 --> 22:55.260
Don't say such discouraging things!

22:55.780 --> 22:57.150
Until the last moment,

22:57.180 --> 22:58.740
there is always hope.

22:58.760 --> 23:01.100
What exactly is this thing on him?

23:01.290 --> 23:02.570
I've seen it before.

23:02.600 --> 23:03.960
I thought it was just a totem.

23:03.980 --> 23:05.140
But it's not,

23:05.170 --> 23:05.900
right?

23:08.930 --> 23:10.200
At this point,

23:10.200 --> 23:11.430
are you still not gonna tell me?

23:11.450 --> 23:12.790
He's currently taking my medicine,

23:12.790 --> 23:13.880
so he's my patient.

23:14.050 --> 23:15.460
If you want me to cure him,

23:15.480 --> 23:17.090
you have to tell me the cause of his illness.

23:17.120 --> 23:18.450
Otherwise, how could I possibly cure him?

23:18.480 --> 23:20.810
Master's illness can't be cured by elixirs.

23:21.160 --> 23:22.280
What does this mean?

23:22.660 --> 23:23.510
Shi Tou.

23:25.000 --> 23:26.000
Take care of Master.

23:27.730 --> 23:28.740
Come with me.

23:41.440 --> 23:42.900
Do you still remember

23:42.980 --> 23:44.310
the secret room you broke into

23:44.310 --> 23:45.510
at the Bright Moon Palace?

23:46.420 --> 23:47.420
Yes.

23:47.450 --> 23:48.590
There were many nameplates

23:48.590 --> 23:50.130
with names engraved on them.

23:50.980 --> 23:52.550
Those names represent

23:52.850 --> 23:54.660
Master's deceased clan members.

23:55.140 --> 23:56.490
[Qi Feng]

23:59.050 --> 24:01.850
I guessed some things when I was in the Outlanders' City.

24:01.870 --> 24:03.080
And I understood

24:03.100 --> 24:04.780
why he was so angry at that time.

24:04.800 --> 24:06.770
But how does this relate to his illness?

24:06.800 --> 24:08.460
To seek revenge,

24:08.730 --> 24:10.250
Master forced himself to grow stronger.

24:10.930 --> 24:12.070
He practiced

24:12.070 --> 24:13.440
all the powerful demonic techniques.

24:14.060 --> 24:15.540
Different techniques clashed,

24:15.620 --> 24:17.410
causing severe backlash.

24:17.980 --> 24:20.630
This is similar to how you wanted to become stronger before.

24:20.850 --> 24:22.180
But the difference is,

24:22.640 --> 24:24.140
back then,

24:24.540 --> 24:25.860
he was all alone,

24:26.520 --> 24:28.260
with no one to teach or protect him.

24:28.860 --> 24:30.980
All he could do was practice

24:31.010 --> 24:32.650
day and night,

24:33.790 --> 24:34.980
risking his life.

24:35.870 --> 24:38.170
The Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal on his chest

24:38.200 --> 24:40.320
is the backlash left from that time.

24:41.000 --> 24:42.620
Every time a star falls,

24:42.650 --> 24:45.760
Master has to bear the burning pain of his heart and soul,

24:47.240 --> 24:48.760
just like now.

24:49.090 --> 24:50.990
Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal?

24:51.190 --> 24:53.010
The name was coined by Cang Shan.

24:53.600 --> 24:54.970
Seven stars,

24:55.190 --> 24:56.660
burning the soul.

24:57.480 --> 24:58.760
It sounds simple,

24:58.890 --> 25:00.590
but it's a deadly danger.

25:00.850 --> 25:02.970
So now, only two stars are still shining.

25:03.550 --> 25:04.660
What does it mean?

25:04.680 --> 25:05.920
It means Master

25:06.470 --> 25:08.630
only has two chances left before the stars fall completely.

25:09.280 --> 25:11.560
Once all seven stars are extinguished,

25:12.260 --> 25:13.920
he will perish.

25:16.290 --> 25:17.640
How can I save him?

25:17.990 --> 25:19.890
You're the only one who can save Master.

25:20.060 --> 25:21.210
As long as the Five Contemplations are gathered

25:21.240 --> 25:22.840
and the divine power of the Wunian Stone is activated,

25:23.050 --> 25:25.090
the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal can be lifted.

25:25.830 --> 25:27.070
This is why you must

25:27.110 --> 25:28.790
activate the Contemplation Stone?

25:29.510 --> 25:30.870
I thought you wanted the divine stone

25:30.900 --> 25:32.010
for some other purpose.

25:32.850 --> 25:33.960
All along this journey, it has been so difficult

25:33.990 --> 25:34.960
and dangerous.

25:35.260 --> 25:37.300
It turns out you just want to save his life.

25:39.290 --> 25:41.340
Master's life is more important than anything.

25:41.820 --> 25:43.570
No matter the cost,

25:44.130 --> 25:46.130
I will do everything in my power to save him.

25:46.980 --> 25:48.750
I've always been curious about one thing.

25:48.790 --> 25:50.670
People all say that the Master of Bright Moon

25:50.720 --> 25:51.990
is ruthless, cold-hearted,

25:52.020 --> 25:53.460
and bloodthirsty.

25:53.480 --> 25:55.240
As the Outlanders' princess,

25:55.270 --> 25:56.990
you're willing to serve him

25:57.010 --> 25:58.770
and remain loyal to him.

25:58.800 --> 26:00.470
Have you never doubted him,

26:00.490 --> 26:01.580
or questioned him?

26:01.940 --> 26:03.170
That's because

26:03.290 --> 26:05.870
you've never truly understood who he is.

26:10.130 --> 26:11.430
Let's go.

26:11.940 --> 26:13.520
You've gained a lot.

26:20.750 --> 26:22.140
She's a beauty.

26:25.630 --> 26:26.550
Hurry up.

26:28.110 --> 26:28.870
Let's go.

26:49.810 --> 26:50.920
When a person dies,

26:51.530 --> 26:53.330
they become nothing more than a speck of dust in the world.

26:53.630 --> 26:54.830
No one will care.

26:56.780 --> 26:58.740
If you're unwilling to be humiliated

26:58.770 --> 26:59.770
or be bullied,

27:03.560 --> 27:05.340
then strive to live on.

27:36.730 --> 27:37.680
Master,

27:37.700 --> 27:39.350
today we, the Wolf Clan, come to pledge allegiance.

27:39.380 --> 27:40.650
The lives of the Rabbit Clan

27:40.670 --> 27:42.430
are our gift to you.

27:50.480 --> 27:52.720
Everyone says that Master is bloodthirsty.

27:53.150 --> 27:54.700
But they don't know

27:55.120 --> 27:56.780
that sometimes he kills

27:56.810 --> 27:58.620
to stop further bloodshed.

28:00.220 --> 28:02.290
Everyone fears the Bright Moon Palace.

28:02.960 --> 28:04.770
But what is truly powerful is never the demons

28:04.830 --> 28:06.350
taken in by the Bright Moon Palace,

28:06.740 --> 28:07.970
but Master himself.

28:08.910 --> 28:10.810
Because only when he is strong enough

28:11.080 --> 28:13.260
can he protect the homeless

28:13.580 --> 28:15.700
and weak little demons

28:16.420 --> 28:18.280
in the predatory Demon Race.

28:27.370 --> 28:28.960
I follow Master,

28:29.160 --> 28:31.290
not because of his strength,

28:31.310 --> 28:33.060
but because of his compassion—

28:34.050 --> 28:36.030
the compassion of Fan Yue, the Master of Bright Moon.

28:36.760 --> 28:38.490
This time, after leaving the Outlanders' City,

28:38.520 --> 28:40.870
Master chose to come to the Unbridled Pavilion

28:39.110 --> 28:43.510
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

28:41.140 --> 28:42.310
because he didn't want the little demons

28:42.310 --> 28:43.400
of the Bright Moon Palace

28:43.400 --> 28:44.880
to see his weakness

28:45.050 --> 28:46.850
and worry for him.

28:45.640 --> 28:51.030
♫Because love is thrilling♫

28:47.060 --> 28:48.300
His endurance

28:48.330 --> 28:50.140
has never been just for you,

28:50.720 --> 28:52.280
but for everyone.

28:51.610 --> 28:55.250
♫If you tear open my heart♫

28:55.910 --> 28:58.220
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

28:56.650 --> 28:59.280
It seems I've never truly understood him.

28:58.770 --> 29:03.260
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

29:00.020 --> 29:01.610
People live with a purpose.

29:02.330 --> 29:03.660
Some live for dignity;

29:04.090 --> 29:05.530
Some live for loyalty.

29:05.830 --> 29:09.560
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

29:06.340 --> 29:08.180
But Master just wants to survive.

29:08.900 --> 29:11.220
I've been by his side for so many years,

29:09.900 --> 29:12.480
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

29:11.280 --> 29:12.550
and I used to think that

29:12.550 --> 29:14.300
nothing could be more important to him than this.

29:12.780 --> 29:14.540
♫I want to tear apart♫

29:15.570 --> 29:18.240
♫This sky for you♫

29:15.580 --> 29:16.960
But now, I'm not so sure.

29:18.030 --> 29:19.530
What exactly are you trying to say?

29:19.150 --> 29:22.120
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

29:19.800 --> 29:21.430
You know what I'm talking about.

29:22.110 --> 29:23.590
All the way here,

29:22.340 --> 29:25.810
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

29:23.610 --> 29:24.580
you know better than I do whether Master

29:24.610 --> 29:26.130
has seen you as a tool

29:26.050 --> 29:29.930
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

29:26.290 --> 29:27.720
or someone he cares about.

29:30.090 --> 29:32.790
♫This moment feels like forever♫

29:34.670 --> 29:36.280
I've put a lot of effort

29:36.300 --> 29:38.910
into the scheme in the Outlanders' City.

29:39.330 --> 29:42.050
I used the strategy of creating a deity to deceive Hua Lin,

29:42.070 --> 29:43.490
the path to becoming king

29:43.510 --> 29:44.950
to lure Wu Zhao,

29:44.970 --> 29:46.370
and the power of the divine sword

29:46.400 --> 29:47.850
to open her heart and take the stone.

29:48.110 --> 29:48.830
Fu Ling,

29:49.710 --> 29:50.560
tell me,

29:51.030 --> 29:52.350
which step in my plan

29:52.940 --> 29:54.380
has a flaw?

29:54.600 --> 29:56.120
Grand Master, your plan

29:56.910 --> 29:58.230
was meticulous

29:58.250 --> 29:58.930
and flawless.

29:58.960 --> 30:00.240
Flawless?

30:04.720 --> 30:06.580
My biggest flaw

30:06.610 --> 30:07.870
was sending you

30:07.900 --> 30:09.660
to the Outlanders' City to oversee it.

30:09.920 --> 30:11.770
It was my fault.

30:11.840 --> 30:13.590
I'm willing to accept your punishment.

30:13.660 --> 30:15.290
Although the plan failed,

30:15.410 --> 30:16.930
it wasn't without gain.

30:17.930 --> 30:19.930
We've already lost,

30:19.950 --> 30:21.790
and you still have excuses?

30:21.860 --> 30:23.260
It's still too early

30:23.290 --> 30:24.700
to say we've lost.

30:24.760 --> 30:25.630
Grand Master,

30:26.090 --> 30:27.370
in the Outlanders' City,

30:27.400 --> 30:29.020
I discovered Fan Yue's secret.

30:30.850 --> 30:32.710
As everyone knows, the Outlanders' City restricts magic,

30:32.740 --> 30:34.140
and spiritual power cannot be used there.

30:34.160 --> 30:35.600
But at the last moment, Fan Yue broke through

30:35.630 --> 30:37.460
the Magic Restriction, unleashed his spiritual power,

30:38.010 --> 30:39.200
and destroyed the altar.

30:39.220 --> 30:41.360
That caused the plan to completely fall apart.

30:41.860 --> 30:44.110
The Wutong Martial Arts Contest has been ongoing for more than 1000 years,

30:44.160 --> 30:46.540
and the Magic Restriction in the Outlanders' City is a 1000-year-old rule.

30:46.560 --> 30:48.160
Although Fan Yue is a Demon King,

30:48.300 --> 30:49.770
he shouldn't have such power.

30:50.180 --> 30:51.030
Fu Ling,

30:51.060 --> 30:52.340
deceiving Grand Master

30:52.360 --> 30:53.760
is an even greater crime.

30:54.550 --> 30:55.840
In the Underground Palace,

30:55.860 --> 30:57.170
I saw with my own eyes

30:57.580 --> 30:58.890
a Big Dipper-shaped totem

30:58.930 --> 31:01.260
glowing on Fan Yue's chest,

31:01.290 --> 31:02.890
with stars flashing on it.

31:03.020 --> 31:04.090
After that,

31:04.110 --> 31:05.890
Fan Yue unleashed his spiritual power.

31:06.970 --> 31:09.650
A Big Dipper-shaped totem?

31:09.920 --> 31:10.750
Yes.

31:11.910 --> 31:13.080
It seems that

31:13.100 --> 31:15.000
those stars

31:15.740 --> 31:17.370
hide some mystery.

31:20.160 --> 31:21.300
Get up.

31:21.480 --> 31:22.610
Find out

31:22.690 --> 31:25.020
what the deal with the stars is.

31:25.220 --> 31:26.670
Yes, Grand Master.

31:26.690 --> 31:28.180
Whether or not the stars were the reason

31:28.210 --> 31:29.670
for Fan Yue's sudden unleashing of spiritual power,

31:30.620 --> 31:32.520
as long as I cultivate this evil insect,

31:32.690 --> 31:33.690
Fan Yue

31:33.710 --> 31:35.200
will no longer be a threat.

31:36.920 --> 31:37.880
Tell me.

31:37.910 --> 31:40.710
This evil insect requires the marrow of 999 demons,

31:40.730 --> 31:42.820
the veins of 999 Eternals,

31:42.850 --> 31:44.600
and the lives of 999 humans

31:44.620 --> 31:45.750
to be combined for its cultivation,

31:45.780 --> 31:47.640
which can capture souls.

31:47.670 --> 31:49.500
No matter how strong the opponent's spiritual power is,

31:49.570 --> 31:51.510
they will be controlled by this evil insect

31:51.830 --> 31:53.520
and become a puppet.

31:53.990 --> 31:55.450
Look at him.

31:55.610 --> 31:56.850
Although he doesn't leave the Cold Spring Palace,

31:56.870 --> 31:59.060
he always helps alleviate my worries.

31:59.270 --> 32:00.730
Since this evil insect

32:00.950 --> 32:02.560
requires so many ingredients,

32:03.200 --> 32:04.010
Fu Ling,

32:04.880 --> 32:06.910
whether you can redeem yourself

32:06.930 --> 32:08.310
depends on you.

32:08.330 --> 32:09.170
Yes.

32:09.200 --> 32:10.640
I will carry out the task.

32:10.660 --> 32:11.760
I heard that Lady Fu Ling

32:11.790 --> 32:13.640
brought a guest back to the Cold Spring Palace.

32:13.930 --> 32:14.930
How about

32:14.960 --> 32:16.330
we offer him as the first sacrifice

32:16.350 --> 32:18.030
to the evil insect?

32:18.500 --> 32:19.840
He is my guest.

32:19.860 --> 32:21.350
I don't need you to meddle.

32:24.120 --> 32:25.770
I promised you that

32:25.790 --> 32:26.870
within a month,

32:26.900 --> 32:28.300
I would make Chong Zhao become a demon.

32:28.330 --> 32:30.260
There are five days left until the one-month deadline.

32:30.280 --> 32:31.280
After five days,

32:31.310 --> 32:33.110
if Chong Zhao hasn't joined the Cold Spring Palace,

32:33.430 --> 32:34.520
I will

32:35.340 --> 32:37.660
offer him to this evil insect myself.

32:39.060 --> 32:40.370
If you fail again,

32:40.940 --> 32:42.420
he will be the first sacrifice,

32:43.660 --> 32:45.600
and you may be the second.

32:47.520 --> 32:48.770
Your insect

32:49.170 --> 32:50.510
can't eat me yet.

33:13.550 --> 33:14.440
Zhao!

33:18.810 --> 33:19.570
Shuo?

33:34.020 --> 33:35.850
You abducted me here?

33:40.490 --> 33:42.090
This is the Cold Spring Palace?

33:42.110 --> 33:43.300
Abduct?

33:43.320 --> 33:44.810
Have you forgotten?

33:44.840 --> 33:47.060
In the Underground Palace of the Outlanders' City, a giant rock collapsed.

33:47.090 --> 33:48.240
If it weren't for me,

33:48.440 --> 33:50.290
you'd already be meat paste by now.

33:50.890 --> 33:52.710
I want to go back to the Outlanders' City.

33:53.020 --> 33:54.920
You're still thinking about going back to save Bai Shuo?

33:54.940 --> 33:56.270
She only has Fan Yue in her heart.

33:56.300 --> 33:56.930
When you were about to die,

33:56.950 --> 33:57.750
did she even care about you?

33:57.780 --> 33:59.450
My business is none of your concern.

34:00.270 --> 34:01.550
None of your concern?

34:11.770 --> 34:13.040
What is this?

34:13.070 --> 34:14.760
My protective demon flower.

34:14.780 --> 34:16.020
It saved you.

34:16.469 --> 34:17.590
Chong Zhao,

34:17.610 --> 34:20.250
you owe me a favor, whether you like it or not.

34:34.030 --> 34:35.760
Even if I have to die,

34:35.790 --> 34:37.870
I won't owe you anything.

34:42.710 --> 34:45.570
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

34:46.409 --> 34:48.679
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

34:49.520 --> 34:50.920
In the Underground Palace of the Outlanders' City,

34:49.770 --> 34:53.310
♫I remember that word of concern♫

34:51.440 --> 34:52.770
Bai Shuo chose for you to die.

34:52.790 --> 34:54.110
But your heart is full of her.

34:54.030 --> 34:57.050
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

34:54.150 --> 34:55.270
I let you survive,

34:55.290 --> 34:56.960
but you hate me deeply.

34:56.989 --> 34:58.490
Since that's the case,

34:57.900 --> 35:00.450
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

34:58.510 --> 35:00.670
I will destroy everything you care about.

35:01.180 --> 35:02.700
You love Bai Shuo,

35:01.470 --> 35:04.670
♫It dried in the wind♫

35:02.720 --> 35:04.390
so I will make her beg for death.

35:04.420 --> 35:05.670
You respect Lanling,

35:05.540 --> 35:07.190
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

35:05.690 --> 35:07.920
so I will make Lanling restless.

35:07.710 --> 35:11.100
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

35:07.950 --> 35:09.510
What exactly

35:10.380 --> 35:12.250
do you want?

35:12.370 --> 35:15.150
♫That year, that year♫

35:12.910 --> 35:14.500
What do I want?

35:16.150 --> 35:19.030
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

35:19.890 --> 35:23.130
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

35:24.120 --> 35:26.480
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

35:26.390 --> 35:28.540
Since I'm in hell,

35:27.490 --> 35:30.750
♫That year, that year♫

35:28.960 --> 35:30.310
Chong Zhao,

35:30.620 --> 35:32.170
come and keep me company.

35:31.230 --> 35:34.390
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

35:35.180 --> 35:38.150
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

35:42.940 --> 35:45.140
This old worm is getting bolder.

35:45.320 --> 35:46.920
He dared to harbor murderous intent

35:46.950 --> 35:48.270
against all the Eternals and demons in the city,

35:48.770 --> 35:50.690
and even captured our head disciple,

35:50.720 --> 35:51.470
Chong Zhao.

35:52.540 --> 35:53.670
Sect Leader, please give the order,

35:54.550 --> 35:56.400
and I will immediately lead the troops to rescue Chong Zhao

35:56.400 --> 35:57.580
and destroy the Cold Spring Palace!

35:57.600 --> 35:58.950
Can you be quiet?

35:59.380 --> 36:01.870
If destroying the Cold Spring Palace were really that easy,

36:01.900 --> 36:03.580
the chaos in the Outlanders' City wouldn't have happened.

36:04.120 --> 36:05.890
But the Cold Spring Palace has always been ruthless.

36:07.140 --> 36:08.190
Will Chong Zhao

36:08.210 --> 36:09.480
be...

36:10.150 --> 36:10.980
No.

36:11.560 --> 36:13.580
If Fu Ling truly wanted to kill Chong Zhao,

36:13.630 --> 36:15.760
she wouldn't have gone through so much effort to save him.

36:15.790 --> 36:18.790
Since the Cold Spring Palace saved Chong Zhao,

36:18.810 --> 36:20.250
perhaps...

36:21.960 --> 36:22.960
Perhaps what?

36:26.260 --> 36:27.530
Perhaps

36:27.560 --> 36:29.040
Chong Zhao is a part

36:29.110 --> 36:30.640
of the Cold Spring Palace's plan.

36:30.660 --> 36:32.570
A part of the plan?

36:33.040 --> 36:35.070
Yan Huo's analysis was right.

36:35.540 --> 36:38.010
The Cold Spring Palace's conspiracy

36:38.040 --> 36:40.080
must be far more complex than it appears.

36:40.950 --> 36:42.880
The sacrifice of all the Eternals and demons in the city

36:42.900 --> 36:45.510
doesn't seem like a pure trick.

36:45.540 --> 36:47.830
The motive behind Zhen Yu's desire to take the Contemplation Stone

36:47.860 --> 36:50.300
must conceal other secrets.

36:51.340 --> 36:53.860
There are too many unknowns

36:53.890 --> 36:56.230
that need to be investigated further.

36:56.380 --> 36:59.110
So, Senior, what's your plan?

36:59.140 --> 37:01.900
This matter is too serious and requires careful consideration.

37:02.040 --> 37:04.730
I will find an opportunity to infiltrate the Cold Spring Palace.

37:04.770 --> 37:06.650
Once I see Chong Zhao,

37:06.670 --> 37:08.310
I'll make a decision.

37:36.740 --> 37:37.490
You're awake?

37:45.330 --> 37:46.560
You've been here all this time?

37:46.990 --> 37:47.910
Of course.

37:50.980 --> 37:52.220
I mean,

37:52.630 --> 37:54.310
of course I should stay by your side.

37:54.330 --> 37:55.490
If you died,

37:55.520 --> 37:57.030
who would help me activate the Contemplation Stone?

38:01.480 --> 38:02.550
Shuo!

38:12.930 --> 38:14.530
The Outlanders' City restricts magic.

38:14.560 --> 38:16.410
How did you break the restriction?

38:16.710 --> 38:17.790
It was just a coincidence.

38:17.810 --> 38:18.810
A coincidence?

38:19.780 --> 38:20.900
Just by coincidence,

38:20.930 --> 38:22.990
you were able to break the thousand-year-old restriction of the Outlanders' City?

38:23.740 --> 38:24.760
Fan Yue,

38:24.780 --> 38:26.370
your ability to break the restriction

38:26.410 --> 38:28.620
is related to your Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal,

38:28.640 --> 38:29.490
right?

38:29.620 --> 38:31.070
Did Tian Huo and Cang Shan told you this?

38:31.770 --> 38:33.810
Don't blame them. I forced them.

38:33.830 --> 38:35.230
Tell me the truth,

38:35.260 --> 38:36.300
did you save me

38:36.320 --> 38:38.330
at the cost of losing a star?

38:38.350 --> 38:39.680
It wasn't just to save you.

38:40.010 --> 38:41.220
If the Outlander King's Sword had been destroyed,

38:41.250 --> 38:42.560
the Outlanders' City would have been destroyed too,

38:42.700 --> 38:43.660
and everyone would have died.

38:43.680 --> 38:44.800
But at that time, the Outlander King's Sword

38:44.830 --> 38:46.270
had already been returned to its stand.

38:46.560 --> 38:47.530
Even if you hadn't blocked for me,

38:48.000 --> 38:49.250
I would have been the only one to die.

38:50.470 --> 38:51.810
You've been asking so many questions.

38:51.890 --> 38:53.280
What answer

38:53.300 --> 38:54.650
are you hoping to hear from me?

38:56.560 --> 38:58.160
How much do you remember about

38:58.200 --> 38:59.470
what happened in the Outlanders' City?

39:01.220 --> 39:02.310
I remember everything.

39:03.330 --> 39:04.180
Then...

39:04.730 --> 39:06.080
what about Mu?

39:08.570 --> 39:10.140
I said I remember everything,

39:10.510 --> 39:12.200
and that means I remember everything.

39:15.690 --> 39:17.200
Master, you're awake?

39:20.880 --> 39:22.520
Did I come at the wrong time?

39:23.990 --> 39:24.900
What do you think?

39:25.120 --> 39:26.250
I came at the wrong time.

39:26.810 --> 39:28.310
You came at just the right time.

39:29.670 --> 39:31.440
Let your master drink the medicine first.

39:31.440 --> 39:32.110
I have something to do.

39:32.110 --> 39:32.920
What is it?

39:35.510 --> 39:37.200
Something that makes the most of things.

39:45.420 --> 39:47.670
Is this what you call making the most of things?

39:48.940 --> 39:51.150
You have such a large place in the Unbridled Pavilion

39:51.170 --> 39:52.630
and you don't do business.

39:52.660 --> 39:54.170
It's a waste to leave it empty.

39:54.440 --> 39:55.800
I might as well use it for alchemy.

39:56.780 --> 39:58.410
I bought this building.

39:59.230 --> 40:00.280
If you want to borrow it,

40:00.820 --> 40:01.580
you have to pay.

40:02.910 --> 40:05.120
Lanling has been exploiting my master like this.

40:05.140 --> 40:07.100
You demons are no different from the Eternals, are you?

40:07.890 --> 40:08.820
Besides,

40:08.850 --> 40:10.210
I'm not doing this for myself.

40:10.230 --> 40:11.570
Then who are you doing it for?

40:11.670 --> 40:13.250
I'm doing it for your master.

40:16.700 --> 40:18.310
I don't like owing favors.

40:18.780 --> 40:20.000
You saved me,

40:20.100 --> 40:21.680
so I should find a way to save you.

40:21.850 --> 40:23.940
Do you think your elixir will be useful?

40:25.920 --> 40:27.850
There's no other way anyway.

40:27.870 --> 40:29.140
Why don't you try mine?

40:29.170 --> 40:31.340
It's better than waiting for your condition to worsen.

40:32.190 --> 40:33.740
You may not trust my medicine skills,

40:34.030 --> 40:35.570
but you trust my master's, right?

40:37.170 --> 40:38.210
Through the turtle shell communication,

40:38.240 --> 40:39.360
my master will guide me personally.

40:39.380 --> 40:40.530
This ensures there will be no problems.

40:59.930 --> 41:01.790
This Pavilion has been out of business for a long time,

41:01.810 --> 41:02.970
so there's dust everywhere.

41:02.990 --> 41:03.760
Tian Huo,

41:03.790 --> 41:04.880
you don't need to stay here.

41:05.660 --> 41:06.820
I can handle it myself.

41:13.020 --> 41:13.820
Huo,

41:13.850 --> 41:15.600
so you knew I was here.

41:17.110 --> 41:18.860
I came here specifically to help you guys.

41:18.890 --> 41:20.050
I can clean these.

41:20.070 --> 41:21.840
It's one thing to follow me all the way from the Outlanders' City

41:21.860 --> 41:22.880
to Ning'an City,

41:22.910 --> 41:24.800
but now you even dare enter the Unbridled Pavilion.

41:24.820 --> 41:26.510
Do you believe I'll break your legs?

41:27.350 --> 41:29.070
So you knew I was following you all along.

41:29.090 --> 41:29.890
That means

41:29.920 --> 41:31.400
you still care about me.

41:32.910 --> 41:33.910
Cang Shan,

41:33.930 --> 41:35.040
kick him out.

41:38.750 --> 41:39.370
Leave!

41:39.390 --> 41:39.910
Leave!

41:39.930 --> 41:40.910
What are you doing?

41:41.800 --> 41:42.560
No, no, no!

41:42.590 --> 41:43.630
No, no, no!

41:43.660 --> 41:44.590
It hurts!

41:44.590 --> 41:46.150
Leave!

41:49.210 --> 41:50.590
It hurts so much!

42:01.650 --> 42:02.820
No, no, no!

42:02.850 --> 42:03.920
If you spill Master Fan's medicine,

42:03.940 --> 42:05.100
it will be a great loss,

42:05.120 --> 42:05.760
right?

42:06.480 --> 42:07.110
I'm here

42:07.110 --> 42:09.150
to work for free in the Unbridled Pavilion.

42:09.170 --> 42:10.170
Washing clothes, cooking meals—

42:10.200 --> 42:11.070
I can do anything.

42:11.090 --> 42:12.260
You can just order me around.

42:13.580 --> 42:14.880
If you don't respond to me,

42:14.900 --> 42:16.010
I'll take it as a yes.

42:24.360 --> 42:25.250
Let go of me.

42:28.610 --> 42:29.450
Hero,

42:29.480 --> 42:30.440
back in the Outlanders' City,

42:30.470 --> 42:32.230
we went through life and death together.

42:32.260 --> 42:33.630
Besides, I even gave the second Heart Flame

42:33.630 --> 42:34.520
to Ms. Bai.

42:34.550 --> 42:35.720
Is this how you treat an old ally?

42:35.760 --> 42:36.600
Who's your ally?

42:36.620 --> 42:38.190
You're just an annoying pest we can't shake off.

42:39.910 --> 42:40.720
Ms. Bai,

42:40.740 --> 42:42.450
please have Shi Tou put me down.

42:42.480 --> 42:43.520
I'm not in charge here

42:43.540 --> 42:44.670
at the Unbridled Pavilion.

42:44.700 --> 42:46.440
You're being modest.

42:46.470 --> 42:47.240
Back in the Outlanders' City,

42:47.260 --> 42:48.820
even Master Fan listened to you.

42:50.820 --> 42:51.880
If you keep being so noisy,

42:51.880 --> 42:53.430
I'll have Cang Shan throw you out.

42:53.450 --> 42:55.050
It has been three times.

43:00.480 --> 43:02.150
Why did you follow us to the Unbridled Pavilion?

43:06.180 --> 43:07.510
I like Huo.

43:07.540 --> 43:08.550
I want to stay with her.

43:08.550 --> 43:10.370
Do you want to die, you stupid fox?

43:10.400 --> 43:12.430
If liking you means I have to die,

43:12.450 --> 43:13.470
then go ahead and kill me.

43:14.440 --> 43:15.810
Are all foxes

43:15.830 --> 43:17.370
unable to keep their thoughts to themselves?

43:17.400 --> 43:18.840
What's there to hide?

43:18.860 --> 43:20.350
If you like someone,

43:20.820 --> 43:22.490
then do your best to be with them.

43:22.520 --> 43:23.330
Besides,

43:23.350 --> 43:24.350
a fox's life is short.

43:24.380 --> 43:25.470
I don't want to miss it.

43:25.850 --> 43:27.390
But you still can't stay.

43:28.220 --> 43:30.110
If you want to stay, you'll have to work.

43:30.430 --> 43:31.670
You'll do all the dirty and tiring work

43:31.670 --> 43:33.750
in the Unbridled Pavilion.

43:33.930 --> 43:35.620
If you make any mistake,

43:35.650 --> 43:36.930
you'll be kicked out immediately.

43:37.770 --> 43:39.040
Master Fan, you're the best!

43:39.230 --> 43:40.420
Thank you, Master Fan!

43:41.710 --> 43:42.340
Huo.

43:46.360 --> 43:47.180
Get to work.

43:48.310 --> 43:49.930
Untie me first!

43:54.290 --> 43:55.120
Ms. Bai,

43:55.150 --> 43:55.960
from now on,

43:55.960 --> 43:57.110
we'll be under the same roof.

44:01.560 --> 44:03.000
Why is your nose bleeding?

44:06.350 --> 44:07.760
Perhaps it's because I stayed up too late yesterday

44:07.780 --> 44:08.820
and got overheated.

44:08.850 --> 44:09.900
Overheated?

44:10.460 --> 44:11.270
That's easy.

44:11.300 --> 44:13.180
I'll make you some herbal tea.
